Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.61,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but don't call me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.48,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped playing karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:22.32,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who showed up late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.71,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't fall asleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:29.67,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're like a little kid on \Nthe night before a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:31.60,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:32.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.93,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get this and also the manju?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:37.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:40.03,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I already bought a gift for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eat these.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.31,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.40,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:50.69,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,worth borrowing money from \Nyour sister to make this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.03,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really that worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.58,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but don't call me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:02.38,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.18,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped playing karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.36,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,An unfamiliar deep voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:12.42,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,with a Fukui accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.48,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't go see him now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.78,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:25.73,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:35.05,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Verse 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:35.05,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}The Sight \Nof a \NMidnight\N Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.55,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.09,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.38,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Taichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.14,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my legs are too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Mine are even longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a trip! \NWhy don't you take in the scenery?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.23,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata probably found a different hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:59.22,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ginza Superstar Sablé
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.24,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a reason to go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.40,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You heartless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.20,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Men don't get touchy-feely \Nwith each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So, Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:09.96,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:12.29,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.03,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.13,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I try to give him chocolate on \NValentine's every year, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.99,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.84,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be giving her \Na serious reply, Dr. Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be considered love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What would be love then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Love is when...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.20,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't fun to be with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.63,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.07,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have fun when you're \Nwith your girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.92,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She listens to me, and she's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So you just wanted to brag?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You should have taken \Nher on a date then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of wasting a day \Noff on a trip to Fukui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:57.75,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.12,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She's ticking me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.16,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even buy a train \Nticket by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.76,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  I forgot about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.78,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's when nothing goes \Nthe way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.52,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:17.77,shiraseki,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Shirasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:17.77,Kanezawa,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kanezawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.49,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're not having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.62,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the window seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.53,Chiha-overlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down!  What's the difference?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.62,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.73,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.63,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If Arata's still living at the same address
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.26,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,that was on his New Year's\N card from two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.26,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,it shouldn't be that far-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:55.72,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:57.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.95,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fukui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.94,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Arata lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.63,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.14,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.64,Chiha-title,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wataya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.64,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go on, Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.02,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously starting \Nto piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.73,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so quiet now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You said that men don't get \Ntouchy-feely with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.11,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm still nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!  Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.95,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.16,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,...a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.16,Chiha-card-TS,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Coward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.56,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.28,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.56,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act all tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:56.54,Chiha-main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like a supermodel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.79,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.13,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.88,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,I live next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.76,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.39,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata?!  Are you Arata's friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:12.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!  We were friends when \NArata lived in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:16.28,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata works at the bookstore by \Nthe station during this time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The station!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.09,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.21,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Back the way we came!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.79,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The station wasn't that far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.93,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:25.36,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's faster than \Ncalling for another taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.78,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And we have to save money \Nfor the train ride home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for telling us where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.69,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Taichi. \N Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.79,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.33,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.54,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:49.38,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.14,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're just gonna stand \Noutside the store anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.24,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Fukui's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.90,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,April's almost over, but the\N cherry's are still blossoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:25.54,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Do I want to see Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.17,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Or do I not want to see Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.22,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We can go home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:43.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:08.75,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.44,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chihaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.33,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.62,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.97,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.84,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave a change of clothes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.86,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.62,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.98,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.92,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.32,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.21,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:34.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, this is a Tokyo specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.70,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Please take some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.47,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:40.68,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:46.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.74,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,How tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.15,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,173.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.82,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I lost by a centimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.62,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also 173.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.76,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you aren't rounding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.53,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You were always a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for letting \Nme use your bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.29,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:11.13,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you wash your hair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.22,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The back of my head \Nwas covered in dirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But my panties were okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.02,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention your panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:16.90,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still in grade school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.40,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They're my panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:19.87,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,My point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.41,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You can wear those clothes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.85,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Once your hair dries, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.75,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:38.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.90,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote a letter for Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.03,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,When we came all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I figured that I \Nwouldn't know what to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.09,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,so it would be easier if I had \Nsomething to read off of!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:49.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play karuta together \Nwith the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.98,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Can we use this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.68,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.19,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite moment when playing karuta
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:14.38,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,comes right before 25 cards are given \Nto each player and they're revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I get so excited when I picture \Nthe good things to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.01,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I picture myself winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:24.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the same for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:30.20,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We were split up when we \Nstarted middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:33.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure that you still \Nplayed karuta by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You were getting better every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:37.96,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.26,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.95,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped playing karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.61,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:55.44,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.17,Chiha-flashback,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses's grandfather \Nis an Eternal Master
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.33,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,who's famous in the karuta world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:12.98,Chiha-flashback,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I immediately knew that his \Ngrandfather had taught him the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:14.83,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.59,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's a load of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.99,Chiha-main,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.11,Chiha-main,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in \Ntrying to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.89,Chiha-main,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Arata we knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:29.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.12,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He must have a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I believe him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.73,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe him, \Ndon't press the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.89,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't come here to see \Nyou kick karuta cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.21,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We won't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!  Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.34,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave these behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.48,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Take them with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:33.06,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I was never good at anything. \NI never had any dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:41.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But Arata told me that if I become \Nthe best karuta player in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I would be the best in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:49.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I can be the best in \Nthe world at something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:59.96,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}as my sleeves are wet with dew
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:59.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Arata stop playing karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.19,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really quit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.19,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.56,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:25.98,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's grandfather, Mr. Wataya, \Nwas an Eternal Karuta Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:30.05,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,and he was the one who taught \NArata to play karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.26,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata loved his grandfather so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.06,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Then, four years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.48,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,his grandfather had a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.81,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata was there to take \Ncare of his grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.82,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,He worked hard to help \Nwith rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:53.30,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, when Arata \Nwas supposed to be home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.89,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,his grandfather suffered a relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.58,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.84,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.29,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandfather suffered an attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.66,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:24.98,champion,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(0,1000)}Champion  Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:22.86,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata had gone to a tournament \Nto reach Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:31.55,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata hasn't touched a card since.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.18,Chiha-main,Yuu,0000,0000,0000,,He can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.03,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:49.13,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,How come you can take cards so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.09,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,You move for the\N "Would the" and "Would this"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.81,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,cards after hearing "would"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.27,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:58.39,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, how can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:04.40,Chiha-flashback,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it's thanks \Nto the karuta god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.40,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,The karuta god?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:12.12,Chiha-flashback,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,If you love karuta and \Nplay it every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:18.01,Chiha-flashback,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,the karuta god will sometimes whisper \Nthe next syllable in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.56,Chiha-flashback,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,You see, my love of karuta is still
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.42,Chiha-flashback,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,just as strong as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:32.48,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,If there truly is a karuta god,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.14,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,he would look just like Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.44,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.53,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote a letter for Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.49,champion,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,If Arata has a cell phone, get his number!!\NImportant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:08.82,champion,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ask if he received my New Year's card this year... \NThe one I screwed up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.06,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ask if he received my New \NYear's card this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:12.46,champion,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}Dr. Harada wants me to send \Nhim a picture of Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.77,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada wants me to send \Nhim a picture of Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:16.73,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to meet Arata \Nat a Kyoto tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.74,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's going to be on a quiz show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.02,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}But only mention this if I \Nhave nothing else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.61,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,This is the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:36.03,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that Arata \Nis like a karuta god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:41.99,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The longer we're apart, \Nthe more you seem like a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:50.08,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.17,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm nothing special.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.65,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.61,champion,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(0,450)}Dr. Harada wants me to send \Nhim a picture of Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.61,champion,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(0,450)}Will I be able to meet Arata \Nat a Kyoto tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.00,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.33,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.64,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Trains are considered public places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.71,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Can you act like a human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:39.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.89,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't have come to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.64,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.79,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.09,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata!  Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.43,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.60,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We can't open this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.10,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to come see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:35.50,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want you to \Nsee what I've become!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.01,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:59.56,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I really missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:11.99,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.40,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that Arata hates karuta now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sit down on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.72,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And stop babbling Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.17,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.41,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And don't get snot everywhere! \NSuck it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:46.97,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hear Arata's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:50.72,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I can be the best in \Nthe world at something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.96,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you start a karuta club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:01.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.57,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If Arata's coming back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,we'll need to make the best \Nkaruta club in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.81,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for his return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.09,club,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's start a competitive karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.09,club,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Please come see Ayase Chihaya in class 1-2!!
